00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,919
I don't get it.

480
00:33:57,080 --> 00:34:00,152
We'll never get back on top
with this kind of hardware.

481
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:01,548
It's old-fashioned.

482
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:05,390
