<i>Shin laundry company.</i>

486
00:34:15,160 --> 00:34:16,798
Yeah. Okay. Thanks.

487
00:34:20,120 --> 00:34:22,918
We've had a little break.

488
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:25,877
Who knows the Hung Fu
Shin laundry company?

489
00:34:27,200 --> 00:34:31,671
My friend tells me that's
where they stash the guns.

490
00:34:32,680 --> 00:34:33,476
Get moving!

491
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:36,756
Not you, Knuckles.
Stay here with me.

492
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:37,636
