me. We're on our own.

497
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,268
What we gonna do?

498
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:11,195
Don't do that! How many
times I got to tell you?

499
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:15,039
Do nothing. Act like
everything was normal.

500
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:20,398
- What does that mean?
- You can't speak Italian?

501
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:22,035
No, boss, I'm Jewish.

502
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:23,833
Then read the translation!

503
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:50,039
- Hey, Fizzy.
- Hey, Bugsy.

504
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:52,755
- Still practicing?
- Still practicing.

505
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:57,356
Suddenly everybody wants
to be in show business.

506
00:36:58,480 --> 00:37:01,438
Hi. Tallulah. I've
come to see Fat Sam.

507
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:03,757
- Is he in?
- No, he's busy.

508
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:06,158
- Hi, Bugsy.
- Hi.

509
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,958
Have a drink while you wait.

510
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,995
Yeah, why not?

511
